	* libbfd.h: Regenerate.
	* elf32-ppc.c (ppc_elf_howto_raw): Add R_PPC_TLSGD and R_PPC_TLSLD.
	(ppc_elf_reloc_type_lookup): Handle new relocs.
	(ppc_elf_check_relocs): Set has_tls_get_addr_call on finding such
	without marker relocs.
