	update.
	(elf_m68k_remove_got_entry_type): Update.
	(elf_m68k_install_rela, dtpoff_base, tpoff): New static functions.
	(elf_m68k_check_relocs): Handle TLS relocations.  Remove unnecessary
	update of sgot->size and srelgot->size.
